    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.02400.003.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Meltonsville Alabama&#8212;</name>
                    <date when="1877-05-20" rend="right">Breaking the Sabbath, May 20 1877<ptr target="loc.02400_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute></salute>       
            </opener>
            
            <p>To Walt Whitman <gap reason="damage" extent="1 or 2 words" quantity="7" unit="chars"/> While most of what I have <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="3" unit="chars"/> written to <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> further amid a sort of <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="4" unit="chars"/>tion of <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> for spells of tedium lonesomeness <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> exceptional&#8212;just now I begin <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="11" unit="chars"/>freeness and soothing or happy <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> out coming from a pure bodily feeling <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> and sleeping today, for the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#ej">remorse</unclear> <gap reason="damage" extent="1 or 2 words" quantity="7" unit="chars"/> interruption of health.) Scenery&#8212; <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> earth, bright sunshine, numerous <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> a brisk, changeable <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nhg">breeze,</unclear> a world <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> every direction&#8212;<hi rend="underline">no <unclear reason="illegible" cert="high" resp="#ab">flowers</unclear></hi>,and I <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> you could <hi rend="underline">forgive me</hi> for this&#8212;but <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> <hi rend="underline">you</hi> what has been a frequent <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> mine&#8212;"if all the things which are <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> done, were left undone, and all the <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="5" unit="chars"/> which are <hi rend="underline">barely undone</hi>, were done, the world every way would present a very different appearance." P.S. Isn't this worth a postage stamp? I, myself, represent "falsehoods," and "the sale of slaves"&#8212;4 or 5 years before my father and mother were married, <hi rend="underline">he</hi> was <hi rend="underline">engaged</hi> to another woman in another State&#8212;going off to <unclear reason="damage" cert="medium" resp="#nhg">Virginia</unclear> <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/> a few slaves, the woman when he <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> towards home with his <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="6" unit="chars"/> was <hi rend="underline">that</hi> <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> another man, and she cried <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/>&#8212;(the tale as it was told me after <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> cook woman who was then a <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/></p>
                
            <p>I am <gap reason="damage" extent="3 or 4 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> put this letter into Paragraphs</p>

            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.02400.004.jpg" type="verso"/>
            
            <p>A neighbor's child was <hi rend="underline">drowned</hi> the other day, but <hi rend="underline">restored</hi>&#8212;its parents temporarily absent from home, returned and <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#ab">found</unclear> their 4 year old boy in the bottom of a shallow well, <hi rend="underline">dead</hi>. I would remark upon the <hi rend="underline"><gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> nation</hi> of distress and happiness <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> felt. <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="4" unit="chars"/> that child and all they <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> sometime he again, and probably after <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> suffering. We should be prepared before <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> for invasions." Yet, <hi rend="underline">you</hi>, probably have <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> with some in the manner you should.&#8212;</p>
            
            <p rend="right">Away with you <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> immortality"&#8212;</p>
            
            <p rend="right">the world has <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> that</p>
            
            <p rend="right">enough already <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> have any-</p>
            
            <p rend="right">thing <hi rend="underline">new</hi>, <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> to say,</p>
            
            <p rend="right">let us have it; but how much</p>
            
            <p>better to do good to our fellow man because he <hi rend="underline">needs</hi> to get his happiness <hi rend="underline">here</hi>.)&#8212;</p>
            
            <p><hi rend="underline">A remarkable</hi> Book has lately appeared, giving the strange history of a Rev. Mr. Sanders in Madison County next this.<ptr target="loc.02400_n2"/> I had heard a little about him before. During 20 years he has had what they call "sleeping spells" lasting from minutes to hours and days. It is hardly to be doubted that he has been <hi rend="underline">seeing and <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="8" unit="chars"/> accurately</hi> in an unusual way. The <hi rend="underline">reason</hi> which possesses him is a mighty <hi rend="underline"><unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#ej">good</unclear></hi><gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="4" unit="chars"/>&#8212;upholds all the "great and glorious <gap reason="illegible" extent="1 word" quantity="9" unit="chars"/> his Orthodox) church&#8212;never <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> language began to write a little <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> gradually
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc.02400.005.jpg" type="recto"/>
            
            came to writing a great deal&#8212;the <hi rend="underline">sermon</hi> always in writing styles Mr Sanders only "<hi rend="underline">my Casket</hi> <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="3" unit="chars"/> doesn't <hi rend="underline">that</hi> sound <hi rend="underline">clergyman-like?</hi>), and <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="4" unit="chars"/> his own name invariably "X + Y = Z <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="3" unit="chars"/> he wrote that he was a <hi rend="underline">school student</hi> <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="4" unit="chars"/> he began this oddity and <hi rend="underline">horrible</hi> <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="4" unit="chars"/> and bodily <hi rend="underline">suffering</hi>&#8212;&#8212;perhaps <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/> studying Algebra. A singing preaching praying <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="4" unit="chars"/> I see that <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="4" unit="chars"/> through accident or design several of <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/> certify to the phenomena, have <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/>ious, or very <hi rend="underline">guarded</hi> language. The <unclear reason="damage" cert="low" resp="#nhg"><hi rend="underline">sermon</hi></unclear> wrote to his "<hi rend="underline">Casket</hi> a letter <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/> announcing that he would leave <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/> sometime, giving him much exhortation <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/> mostly Paul's farewell advice to <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="6" unit="chars"/>&#8212;I believe.&#8212;I have not the Book <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/> of course I have consulted Abercrombie <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="4" unit="chars"/>. Phil. (which I <hi rend="underline">happened</hi> to buy long <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/>&#8212;Dreaming, Somnambulist, Insanity, Coincidences, his own absurd reasoning all there. I have studied, and studied, and studied&#8212;taking it easy tho'&#8212;thought I ought to go to see Sanders; till I saw the <hi rend="underline">D</hi>&#8212; had left him. From May till Sept the man remained well. Take note that I have been fearing that <hi rend="underline">you</hi> may be <unclear reason="damage" cert="high" resp="#nhg">to some</unclear> degree <hi rend="underline">seduced</hi> by the professor <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/> people's <hi rend="underline">growing kindness.</hi> (Walt! <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/> be a renegade&#8212;you must stand by <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/> "wicked and <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="4" unit="chars"/> and <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/>&#8212;<hi rend="underline">please stand by them</hi> <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="4" unit="chars"/> <hi rend="underline">let no blandishments</hi> <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="11" unit="chars"/></p> 
                <p>&#42;Are you not <hi rend="underline">ambiguous</hi> in "Two Rivulets" latter part note "Freed</p>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc.02400.006.jpg" type="verso"/>
            
            <p>I have never read Books on "Political Economy", but during the last year have studied more on the subject of <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="4" unit="chars"/> Profit on Capital&#8212;concluded that perhaps no <hi rend="underline"><gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> at all</hi> would be nearer right&#8212;at least <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> to be very small indeed&#8212;the <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> <hi rend="underline">opportune</hi> for I have various <gap reason="damage" extent="5 words" quantity="20" unit="chars"/> with in mostly poor, who <gap reason="damage" extent="5 words" quantity="20" unit="chars"/> prepared to pay Interest&#8212;I can <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> more <hi rend="underline">pity</hi> borrowers and renters.&#8212;</p>
            
            <p><del>You old rascal!</del> you <gap reason="damage" extent="1 or 2 words" quantity="8" unit="chars"/> have declined to say you would advise me about books to buy&#8212;I <choice><sic>would'nt</sic><corr>wouldn't</corr></choice> have <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> much&#8212;I shall not have much <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> to spare to buy any books&#8212;(I will <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="3" unit="chars"/> always have enough to buy all that <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/>) I did want to ask if you thought I would <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> pleased and some profited by <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> <hi rend="underline">Emerson's.</hi></p> 
            
            <p>As I only made half <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> year, and <hi rend="underline">price of cotton</hi> seems to have <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nhg">settled</unclear> down permanently, I spent last year several times as much as I made&#8212;also during same time became pretty well convinced that a good deal of debts owing to me will never be paid. <hi rend="underline">I dont feel so rich</hi> as I did 3 years ago, but if <hi rend="underline">so resolute</hi> a man, so <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> lastingly thoughtful a man, can't <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> along well enough to satisfy such <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> <hi rend="underline">please</hi> to <gap reason="damage" extent="1 word" quantity="5" unit="chars"/> me <hi rend="underline">who should</hi>? <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> suppose that I shall find myself <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> <hi rend="underline">ingenious?</hi> Make the Phil. Weekly <hi rend="underline">Times</hi>. <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> this year, &#190; corn, &#188; cotton <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"/> <hi rend="underline">barely</hi> send this or <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="13" unit="chars"></gap></p>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf003r" facs="loc.02400.001.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <pb xml:id="leaf003v" facs="loc.02400.002.jpg" type="verso"/>
            
